## 7. 完全卸载

```
launchctl bootout gui/$(id -u)/com.bisdom.hiagent_sidecar
launchctl bootout gui/$(id -u)/com.bisdom.hiagent_tunnel
rm ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bisdom.hiagent_sidecar.plist
rm ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.bisdom.hiagent_tunnel.plist
rm ~/hiagent_sidecar ~/hiagent_plugin.log ~/hiagent_plugin.pid
rm ~/hiagent_tunnel.log ~/get_tunnel_url
```

主项目（openclaw-model-bridge）零残留——卸载完系统回到集成前的状态。

